Destructor ran as fast as he could with proto on his back. He was going fast 
just from the plasma wounds. He was never going to catch this in time. But he 
got an idea. he transformed and grabbed proto. Heemptied his plasma gun and 
poured Proto into it. he fired it and it flew into the shot. Proto glowed and 
formed a square metal object. His form of stasis lock. Destructor picked him 
up sending a comm to Megatron. "I wish to request some energon to save this 
bots life. he after all saved yours!"

--part1_16e.10327e0e.2a5b4a86_boundary
